<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="0t" end="20000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"></p>
<p begin="199300000t" end="217700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">成功进行了人体炼成？</p>
<p begin="234800000t" end="249800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">只是传闻而已</p>
<p begin="251900000t" end="264000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">是何方神圣来的?</p>
<p begin="271100000t" end="307800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">听说是在一户叫汉博甘古的人家里做事的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="326100000t" end="332800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">叫什么名字</p>
<p begin="348200000t" end="356600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">居德</p>
<p begin="378000000t" end="407000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">盲目的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="445800000t" end="483800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">居德 今天在学校量了身高体重哦</p>
<p begin="488400000t" end="516300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">我在班上女生中是个子最高的哦</p>
<p begin="525500000t" end="559700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">你可真是 长大了啊</p>
<p begin="560100000t" end="573000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">罗莎莉小姐</p>
<p begin="583500000t" end="609700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">这孩子自从开始上学以后</p>
<p begin="610600000t" end="633900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">尽学些捣蛋的鬼点子 真伤脑筋啊</p>
<p begin="638900000t" end="655190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">也不知道是像谁</p>
<p begin="675200000t" end="692300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">如果是像夫人您的话</p>
<p begin="694400000t" end="718600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">一定会变得美貌出众吧</p>
<p begin="767400000t" end="797400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">居德大人 有人想见您</p>
<p begin="797400000t" end="809100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">要领进来吗</p>
<p begin="817000000t" end="841200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">居然会有人来见我 真是难得</p>
<p begin="846200000t" end="868700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">好像是旅行中的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="899200000t" end="916300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">炼金术师?</p>
<p begin="924600000t" end="944700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">我还真想会会</p>
<p begin="955500000t" end="971800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">那么他叫什么名字呢</p>
<p begin="995100000t" end="1061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">爱德华·艾尔利克氏和阿尔方斯·艾尔利克氏</p>
<p begin="1169500000t" end="1191600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">真是栋豪宅啊 哥哥</p>
<p begin="1197000000t" end="1236600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">就算雇佣二三十个炼金术师都不成问题啊</p>
<p begin="1239500000t" end="1275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">你是说宅子很大 还是说这家人很富裕</p>
<p begin="1276200000t" end="1288700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">两方面都有</p>
<p begin="1367200000t" end="1400500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">怎么 我们干了什么吗</p>
<p begin="1405500000t" end="1425100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">可能他以为我们是小偷</p>
<p begin="1426000000t" end="1443100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">什么小偷啊</p>
<p begin="1490000000t" end="1499000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">你是...</p>
<p begin="1499000000t" end="1525200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">全身铠甲哇 变态哇</p>
<p begin="1531100000t" end="1544800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">变态...</p>
<p begin="1545000000t" end="1568000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">铠甲 铠甲 铠甲...</p>
<p begin="1566900000t" end="1580700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">这小鬼是哪儿来的</p>
<p begin="1586500000t" end="1596100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="1650000000t" end="1791000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">变态 铠甲 变态 铠甲...</p>
<p begin="1682900000t" end="1712500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">是爱德华先生和阿尔方斯先生吧</p>
<p begin="1716300000t" end="1730400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我就是居德</p>
<p begin="1735400000t" end="1782600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我是爱德华 那边被当成玩具的就是我弟弟阿尔方斯</p>
<p begin="1818400000t" end="1842200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">如你所见 我眼睛不方便</p>
<p begin="1842200000t" end="1859300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">所以一般不外出</p>
<p begin="1863100000t" end="1908500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">也没什么机会和其他炼金术师沟通交流</p>
<p begin="1913100000t" end="1942300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">非常感谢您特地来这一趟</p>
<p begin="1992400000t" end="2012000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">手太硬吓到你了吗</p>
<p begin="2016600000t" end="2045300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">哪里 并不是这个意思</p>
<p begin="2049500000t" end="2075800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我也是因为听说了居德先生的事</p>
<p begin="2075800000t" end="2110000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">所以想跟你好好聊一聊炼金术</p>
<p begin="2113000000t" end="2129000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">传闻吗</p>
<p begin="2135800000t" end="2175900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">说你长年侍奉于这户汉博甘古人家之类的</p>
<p begin="2181300000t" end="2209700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">技术堪匹敌国家炼金术师之类的</p>
<p begin="2210500000t" end="2245500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你用自己的技术将汉博甘古从存亡危机中拯救出来之类的</p>
<p begin="2263100000t" end="2297700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">并且还进行过人体炼成 之类的</p>
<p begin="2325600000t" end="2346900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">不过是空穴来风罢了</p>
<p begin="2350200000t" end="2391900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">搞不好那些流言中 夹杂着一两件真事呢</p>
<p begin="2416500000t" end="2447400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">能带罗莎莉小姐离开一下吗</p>
<p begin="2457800000t" end="2477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">是啊 罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="2496200000t" end="2515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">不要 我要和铠甲一起玩</p>
<p begin="2517100000t" end="2533700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">不可以 大小姐</p>
<p begin="2535400000t" end="2554600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">客人有重要的事要谈</p>
<p begin="2558800000t" end="2571300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">就不要</p>
<p begin="2572090000t" end="2583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">大小姐</p>
<p begin="2612600000t" end="2632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">阿尔也跟她去吧</p>
<p begin="2634700000t" end="2642200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">真的?</p>
<p begin="2668900000t" end="2688900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我带你在宅子里转转</p>
<p begin="2695600000t" end="2724800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我知道啦 你别拽我啦</p>
<p begin="2747300000t" end="2769000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">在这里说话也不方便 到亭子去吧</p>
<p begin="2841100000t" end="2881600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我不喜欢兜圈子 就开门见山地说吧</p>
<p begin="2889900000t" end="2929100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">你进行过人体炼成吗 有还是没有</p>
<p begin="2937500000t" end="2950000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">你知道了又能怎样</p>
<p begin="2956700000t" end="2972500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">仅作参考而已</p>
<p begin="2995000000t" end="3016700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我的双眼都被夺走了</p>
<p begin="3030500000t" end="3053000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我是被夺走了左腿和弟弟</p>
<p begin="3070500000t" end="3079300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">右手呢</p>
<p begin="3085100000t" end="3093000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">这个?</p>
<p begin="3102600000t" end="3135200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">这是用来炼成了弟弟的灵魂</p>
<p begin="3165200000t" end="3181100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">我们是同命相怜啊</p>
<p begin="3183600000t" end="3203200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">虽然是不情愿的同命相怜啊</p>
<p begin="3227400000t" end="3239900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">这下我放心了</p>
<p begin="3245300000t" end="3253200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">居德</p>
<p begin="3256500000t" end="3277400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">夫人 没关系</p>
<p begin="3282400000t" end="3312000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">他并不是来对我做什么的</p>
<p begin="3330800000t" end="3369200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">原来真的以为我们会对你做什么啊</p>
<p begin="3382900000t" end="3424600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">既然这点明白了 那我们就能打开天窗说亮话了</p>
<p begin="3428000000t" end="3446700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">你还有什么想问的事吗</p>
<p begin="3463400000t" end="3490500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">外界传闻你成功进行了人体炼成 是真的吗</p>
<p begin="3536000000t" end="3579400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">爱德华先生 你已经见过那个成果了</p>
<p begin="3599400000t" end="3632800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">罗莎莉 那孩子就是炼成的结果</p>
<p begin="3667400000t" end="3681600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">空的</p>
<p begin="3700700000t" end="3738700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">别怕 罗莎莉 这个说来话长</p>
<p begin="3741600000t" end="3770000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">好厉害 仅靠一副铠甲就可以动呢</p>
<p begin="3772900000t" end="3788300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="3792100000t" end="3804600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">喂</p>
<p begin="3810000000t" end="3837100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">就是一副铠甲而已 也能进行思考啊</p>
<p begin="3851300000t" end="3893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">居德说过 只有人类才会思考</p>
<p begin="3900900000t" end="3914300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">你没被吓到吗</p>
<p begin="3919700000t" end="3956000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">是有点吃惊 不过我见过更厉害的</p>
<p begin="3969300000t" end="4002700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">这样啊 所以才会找上居德</p>
<p begin="4005200000t" end="4014000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">原来如此</p>
<p begin="4027300000t" end="4034800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">你跟我来</p>
<p begin="4050300000t" end="4068600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">是你的话就可以让你看看</p>
<p begin="4074000000t" end="4089500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">罗莎莉的秘密</p>
<p begin="4100300000t" end="4136600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">我进行人体炼成已经是三年前的事了</p>
<p begin="4145800000t" end="4173700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">如你所见 她现在成长得非常健康</p>
<p begin="4178300000t" end="4193700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">果然是可能实现的啊</p>
<p begin="4199200000t" end="4224200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">爱德华先生失败了吗</p>
<p begin="4253800000t" end="4273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">我为了炼成妈妈</p>
<p begin="4286300000t" end="4297200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">跟我一起来的铠甲</p>
<p begin="4301800000t" end="4337200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">刚才也说了 那是我弟弟</p>
<p begin="4338900000t" end="4360200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">就是你说炼成了灵魂的...</p>
<p begin="4381400000t" end="4412300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">所以 至少我希望他能恢复原样</p>
<p begin="4412300000t" end="4444800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">拜托你 告诉我人体炼成的方法</p>
<p begin="4469400000t" end="4489400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">关于这件事我们无可奉告</p>
<p begin="4489900000t" end="4502000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">为什么</p>
<p begin="4507400000t" end="4533200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">居德是我们家的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="4538200000t" end="4578700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">因此他的能力仅为汉博甘古家所用</p>
<p begin="4583300000t" end="4612900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">不能将此秘术外传</p>
<p begin="4617500000t" end="4630400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">怎么可以...</p>
<p begin="4634600000t" end="4679200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">请您放弃吧 这是我去世的丈夫所说过的话</p>
<p begin="4720500000t" end="4752200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">毕竟是主人的意思 唯有这件事我不能告诉您</p>
<p begin="4770600000t" end="4792700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">非常抱歉帮不上您的忙</p>
<p begin="4796000000t" end="4850200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">而且因为眼睛的缘故 也不可能再给你画出当时的炼成阵</p>
<p begin="4871500000t" end="4905300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">我会真心祈祷你们能恢复原来的身体</p>
<p begin="4995000000t" end="5003300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">请问...</p>
<p begin="5007900000t" end="5017100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">不行</p>
<p begin="5023700000t" end="5043300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我还什么都没说呢</p>
<p begin="5049600000t" end="5062100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">爱德华先生</p>
<p begin="5078800000t" end="5102100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">请您打消进行人体炼成的念头吧</p>
<p begin="5107100000t" end="5136790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">我决定了要让弟弟恢复原样</p>
<p begin="5139700000t" end="5157990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">所以希望居德先生能再次...</p>
<p begin="5159290000t" end="5173500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">就算你知道了也没用</p>
<p begin="5181400000t" end="5196400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">怎么会没用呢</p>
<p begin="5199290000t" end="5210200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">他的确是成功了啊</p>
<p begin="5211000000t" end="5221790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">没用的</p>
<p begin="5316500000t" end="5349900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">我知道了 我带阿尔回去</p>
<p begin="5378300000t" end="5401200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">好像是和罗莎莉去玩了吧</p>
<p begin="5412000000t" end="5427000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我自己找吧</p>
<p begin="5429000000t" end="5440000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">可以吧</p>
<p begin="5445000000t" end="5452000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">没关系</p>
<p begin="5461300000t" end="5497500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不过 请千万不要进二楼里面的那个房间</p>
<p begin="5502500000t" end="5529200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">那是我与去世的丈夫充满回忆的房间</p>
<p begin="5535000000t" end="5546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">是是</p>
<p begin="5679400000t" end="5713600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">她说千万不能进里面那个房间</p>
<p begin="5720700000t" end="5749900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">你说不让进我偏要进</p>
<p begin="5834100000t" end="5847500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">快点 快点</p>
<p begin="5864200000t" end="5892100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">阿尔那家伙 要到哪儿去</p>
<p begin="5974700000t" end="5996400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">罗莎莉 有客人哦</p>
<p begin="6143600000t" end="6176600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">这就是居德用人体炼成找回的罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="6230800000t" end="6245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">罗莎莉你还好吗</p>
<p begin="6258300000t" end="6268300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">你不害怕吗</p>
<p begin="6272100000t" end="6283700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">我习惯了</p>
<p begin="6290800000t" end="6319600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">可是 这是罗莎莉的话 你又是谁</p>
<p begin="6322900000t" end="6374700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">对 我啊 是从孤儿院里领来的假罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="6380100000t" end="6408900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">因为我长得像真的罗莎莉才被领养的</p>
<p begin="6411800000t" end="6431000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">我一直在扮演着她</p>
<p begin="6442700000t" end="6466800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我的真名是艾米</p>
<p begin="6472700000t" end="6488100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">太复杂了</p>
<p begin="6500600000t" end="6519800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">不过 只要演好我的角色</p>
<p begin="6523600000t" end="6547300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">我就能有热腾腾的饭菜吃 有漂亮的衣服穿</p>
<p begin="6550300000t" end="6574900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">还能拥有和蔼可亲的家人</p>
<p begin="6582000000t" end="6596100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">这里就是天堂</p>
<p begin="6619100000t" end="6647400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">罗莎莉你头发总是这么漂亮 真好</p>
<p begin="6648700000t" end="6658700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">就像丝一样</p>
<p begin="6690800000t" end="6707900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">动...动了</p>
<p begin="6712900000t" end="6736700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">你不是也和她差不多吗</p>
<p begin="6736700000t" end="6751700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">有什么好害怕的</p>
<p begin="6760900000t" end="6777600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">她...她活着吗</p>
<p begin="6787600000t" end="6812200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我也不知道她算不算活着</p>
<p begin="6821400000t" end="6843900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">罗莎莉一直就是这样</p>
<p begin="6850100000t" end="6906000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">不过在她身体里的到底是不是真正的罗莎莉 谁都不知道</p>
<p begin="6910200000t" end="6950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">也许里面并不是她 而是其它什么东西</p>
<p begin="6991500000t" end="7009900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">一定是真的</p>
<p begin="7021600000t" end="7072900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">恩 因为真正的罗莎莉就在这里</p>
<p begin="7076200000t" end="7112900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">所以我没法成为这家人真正的孩子</p>
<p begin="7140000000t" end="7148800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">艾米</p>
<p begin="7155400000t" end="7171700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">可是如果做回艾米的话</p>
<p begin="7173000000t" end="7191700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">就只能待在孤儿院那阴暗的角落</p>
<p begin="7194700000t" end="7218000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">只能玩玩木棍过日子</p>
<p begin="7254300000t" end="7271800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">你还是进来了</p>
<p begin="7344000000t" end="7376100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我必须要遵守已去世的丈夫所说的话</p>
<p begin="7380300000t" end="7414000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">可我还是希望你看到这些</p>
<p begin="7434500000t" end="7453700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">所以你才故意叫我别进来</p>
<p begin="7527100000t" end="7548300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">眼睛 眼睛烧焦了</p>
<p begin="7555400000t" end="7575000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">夫人 老爷</p>
<p begin="7590900000t" end="7633000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">罗莎莉小姐呢 我什么也看不见了</p>
<p begin="7633800000t" end="7646400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">请告诉我</p>
<p begin="7651800000t" end="7674300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">我的理论是否完美</p>
<p begin="7677200000t" end="7691000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">大小姐她...</p>
<p begin="7702700000t" end="7711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">居德</p>
<p begin="7716400000t" end="7732300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">放心吧</p>
<p begin="7735600000t" end="7754000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">你的炼成非常完美</p>
<p begin="7764000000t" end="7793600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">女儿已经回到了我们的身边</p>
<p begin="7802800000t" end="7821900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">就像以前一样</p>
<p begin="7842400000t" end="7860300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">罗莎莉小姐</p>
<p begin="7904500000t" end="7950400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">居德先生从上代主人的时候起就是这家的炼金术师</p>
<p begin="7950400000t" end="7995500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">最初不过是作为研究者和出资者的关系</p>
<p begin="7998000000t" end="8026700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">不知何时 变得像一家人一样亲密了</p>
<p begin="8032600000t" end="8068900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">所以 他也许是不忍再看到夫人</p>
<p begin="8068900000t" end="8113500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">因失去独生女罗莎莉小姐而伤心欲绝的样子吧</p>
<p begin="8129300000t" end="8190700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">不 居德先生本人也是想让罗莎莉小姐复活的吧</p>
<p begin="8216100000t" end="8258600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">因为夫人和罗莎莉小姐 对他来说就像家人一样</p>
<p begin="8269100000t" end="8293300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">管家先生 你也...</p>
<p begin="8300300000t" end="8340000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">我们所有的佣人都没有告诉他真相</p>
<p begin="8355800000t" end="8387100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">而且今后恐怕也会继续隐瞒下去</p>
<p begin="8390400000t" end="8427600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">只要大家能像以前一样 那就足够了</p>
<p begin="8436700000t" end="8458000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">来 回房间去吧</p>
<p begin="8459300000t" end="8476400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">罗莎莉小姐</p>
<p begin="8483000000t" end="8490100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">恩</p>
<p begin="8514700000t" end="8526000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">拜拜</p>
<p begin="8543500000t" end="8558900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">拜拜 罗莎莉</p>
<p begin="8629000000t" end="8646100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">大家都是好人啊</p>
<p begin="8650700000t" end="8656500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">恩</p>
<p begin="8718700000t" end="8750800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">可是 大家都无法被救赎</p>
</div>
